title: Baadshah
subTitle: An amateur detective, Raj, goes by the nickname of Baadshah. But this name soon causes a misunderstanding that lands him in the middle of a conspiracy to assassinate the chief minister of Goa.

title: Bombay Boys
subTitle: Three Indian men raised in the West meet in Mumbai to fulfil separate goals. Krishna tries to make it big in Bollywood, Ricardo searches for his long-lost brother and Xerxes rediscovers his roots.

title: Krishna Arjun
subTitle: After hearing the news of his mother's death, a man travels home to find his brother has been arrested for rape and murder. He sets out to uncover the truth.

title: Sherdil Bharat
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Katilon Ke Kaatil
subTitle: Traumatised by her murder of her husband and the abduction of her two sons, a woman spends her life looking for her family. Things take a turn when two men arrive at her house with a family heirloom.

title: Mr. Natwarlal
subTitle: When Natwar's elder brother is framed for bribery, he decides to avenge his brother's humiliation and thus poses as a crime lord.

title: Khudgarz
subTitle: Sita raises her son, Bihari, and his friend Amar as her own and the two treat each other like brothers. However, Amar's father is not too fond of Bihari, and he tries to create a rift between the two.

title: Main Khiladi Tu Anari
subTitle: A Bombay police officer seeks revenge when a drug dealer kills his brother. However, things get complicated when a film star begins to tag along, so that he can research a film role.

title: Anushka
subTitle: A couple's peaceful night together is shattered by strange and terrifying supernatural events. They must confront the malevolent spirits haunting them to survive the night.

title: Anushka
subTitle: A couple's peaceful night together is shattered by strange and terrifying supernatural events. They must confront the malevolent spirits haunting them to survive the night.

title: Mera Faisla
subTitle: Raj wishes to marry Rati but faces humiliation from her father due to the stigma associated with his lineage. Soon, he decides to join the police force to restore his family's honour.

title: Maharaja
subTitle: Bored by his monotonous lifestyle, Mahadevan, a middle-aged family man, longs to lead a modern life. However, everything begins to fall apart when he chooses to change his way of living.

title: Kundan
subTitle: Thakur Shamsher Singh, a wealthy criminal, tries to befriend a newly-appointed police officer in order to gain his favour, only to find out that the policeman is immune to his tactics.

title: Avinash
subTitle: Avinash's life turns upside down when he is pursued by dangerous men for a video tape he accidentally acquired. His family and his memory become victim to this murderous pursuit, further complicating things.

title: Rustum
subTitle: Abhishek Bhargav, a police officer, decides to avenge the death of his friend, DCP Bharath. When his investigation lands him in Bengaluru, he discovers the roots of an organ trading mafia.

title: Dhadkan
subTitle: Anjali and Dev's love story faces a harsh twist when Anjali is forced to marry Ram. Years later, Dev returns to rekindle their romance, only to find that Anjali has grown to love her husband.

title: Pehchaan
subTitle: Shankar seeks revenge on the judge who convicted him by kidnapping his wife. The judge is unaware of his wife's pregnancy and disowns the child as he thinks she is the result of his wife's infidelity.

title: Lal Baadshah
subTitle: Lal Singh, a righteous and helpful man, clashes against Dayal Singh, a powerful personality. However, things get complicated when a hidden treasure is involved and Lal's tragic past is disclosed.

title: Khiladi
subTitle: A group of four friends decide to play a prank involving the fake kidnapping of one of them and asking for ransom from her father. However, things become complicated when she actually ends up dead.

title: Khiladi
subTitle: A group of four friends decide to play a prank involving the fake kidnapping of one of them and asking for ransom from her father. However, things become complicated when she actually ends up dead.

title: Teri Kasam
subTitle: Dolly, a rich and spoilt woman, falls for Tony, a poor musician, and marries him. However, her arrogance begins to create problems in their marital life.

title: Humjoli
subTitle: A misunderstanding leads to two college friends, Madhu and Sidhu turning bitter towards each other. However, circumstances reunite them for a friend.

title: Azad Desh Ka Andha Kanoon
subTitle: An honest policemen is forced to choose between duty and family when his brother is caught as part of a gang producing blue-films. He must also protect a witness whose life is threatened.

title: Maati Maangey Khoon
subTitle: Hariya is clueless about his parents and discovers that his family was destroyed by Thakur Balram Singh. He vows to take revenge, especially after his friend, who is Balram's nephew, also opposes him.

title: Devta
subTitle: An ordinary taxi driver becomes part of a notorious gang through a twist of fate and takes on the role of a terrifying assassin.

title: Shakthi: The Power
subTitle: Nandini and Shekhar's visit to India turns tragic when they meet his violent family. After losing Shekhar, Nandini fights to save their son and escape back home.

title: Khoon Bhari Maang
subTitle: Widowed Aarti falls prey to Sanjay's vicious plan of getting married to him. Later, with the help of her best friend Nandini, he drowns Aarti and seizes her wealth but she survives and seeks revenge.

title: Bol Radha Bol
subTitle: While Kishen enjoys village life and romance with Radha, a sinister doppelganger plots. Upon returning home, he'll discover his identity and life stolen by this malevolent impostor.
